that the values of TC and BMI have been significantly reduced at the second examination
compared with the values measured at the first examination (<italic>p</italic>&#x0003c;0.001,
<italic>p</italic>=0.001 respectively). The values of HDL increased with statistic
significance (<italic>p</italic>&#x0003c;0.001). On the other hand, the comparison between the
